<div style="border:solid 2px #191c23; background:#2f3442; padding:10px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h1 id="toc0"><span><tt><em><span style="color: #137f00">chatConnect v3.0</span></em></tt></span></h1>
<p><span style="font-size:80%;"><tt><em><strong><span style="color: #137f00">私人连接实用程序</span></strong></em></tt></span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<table style="border: none;">
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: ;eft; font-family: monotype; color:#ffffff;">┌──────────────────────────<br />
»<tt><em><strong><span style="color: #d051ff">'n06ody</span></strong> 已加入大厅</em></tt><br />
└──────────────────────────</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">好哇，<span class="ruby">没有人<span class="rt">Nobody</span></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;">&lt;einBoot&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">哟嚯，没有人</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">发生了什么</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">有什么问题？这电话会议真是非常早</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;">&lt;'n06ody&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">简单来说，我有麻烦了</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;">&lt;einBoot&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">啊，该死</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">你在哪</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;">&lt;einBoot&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">这一点都不好</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;">&lt;'n06ody&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">我现在正呆在一家网咖里</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">在宾夕法尼亚州的中部</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">我可以派些人来接你。不管怎么说，之前boat被从伏尔加格勒救了出来</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;">&lt;einBoot&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">那不是我的错</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;">&lt;'n06ody&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">呐，这将会有很多麻烦</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;">&lt;einBoot&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">不管怎么说，问题是什么</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;">&lt;'n06ody&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">一些南美准军事人员，boat。那是军阀的部队，也许吧？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">大体上来说，我应该还好</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">大体上？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;">&lt;einBoot&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">我想我知道你的意思了，没有人能让我找到张照片</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;">&lt;'n06ody&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">所以说，我发现他们在受关注地区四处窥探</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">事实上，更多的是他们在窥探中发现我窥探他们</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">是不是说这与最近发生在宾州的一个异常事故有确切的关联？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">不是巧合吗？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;">&lt;'n06ody&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">啊呀，不是个巧合，我可以很肯定的说</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">操。会是亚洲佬走漏消息的吗？我很确定没有人在这里</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;">&lt;einBoot&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">你认为他们会知道他们在找什么东西吗？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;">&lt;'n06ody&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">嗯，我十分确定他们会的。他们没有绕多少弯路</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">就像其他军队常常干的 :P</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">你怎么想，boat？关于泛美团体，你似乎比我们知道的更多。</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;">&lt;einBoot&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">不大确定，说实在，窝可能会知道的更多，但没有人能证实我的怀疑</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">sakal，你看起来比平时更焦虑</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">我知道，就是有些紧张。如果我问的问题没有礼貌的话，抱歉</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;">&lt;'n06ody&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">我明白。你只是想要确保我还好。多谢</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;">&lt;einBoot&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">等等，我想我找到他们了</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">草他娘的图片下载不了，等等几分钟</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">继续吧，他们抓住你后发生了什么？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;">&lt;'n06ody&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">那家伙对我大喊大叫</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">不知道说的是葡萄牙语还是西班牙语</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">基本上我定住他后再偷走了他的摩托车</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#d051ff;"></td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">草他的我从那里跑了出来后就结束了</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#c6c900;">&lt;einBoot&gt;</td>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ffffff;">找到一张新图片</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;; color:#ff1e1e;">&lt;sakaali&gt;</td>
